---
// Hero — copy "manguito-forward". Headline juega con el nombre.
// Hero shot: dashboard real de la app con halo decorativo de marca.
---

<section class="bg-hero-glow relative overflow-hidden pt-32 pb-20 sm:pt-44 sm:pb-28 lg:pt-48 lg:pb-32">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl items-center gap-14 px-6 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1.15fr] lg:gap-16">
    <div class="text-center lg:text-left">
      <span
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-white/70 px-3.5 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] backdrop-blur"
      >
        <span class="inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)]"></span>
        Hecho en Argentina · pesos, dólares y todo lo del medio
      </span>

      <h1
        class="mt-7 text-5xl font-bold leading-[1.02] tracking-tight text-[var(--color-ink)] sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl xl:text-[5rem]"
      >
        Tus finanzas,
        <span class="text-brand-gradient">sin un mango</span>
        menos.
      </h1>

      <p
        class="mx-auto mt-7 max-w-xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] sm:text-xl lg:mx-0"
      >
        Reenviame los mails del banco. Subí el resumen de la tarjeta. Mandale
        un mensaje a Manguito. Como te quede más cómodo: tus gastos se
        cargan solos.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-9 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 sm:flex-row lg:justify-start">
        <a
          href="https://app.sinunmango.com.ar"
          class="bg-brand-gradient inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl px-7 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-[color:var(--color-accent)]/20 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 sm:text-lg"
        >
          Probar en la web
          <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>

        <!-- Botón Google Play. Color negro estándar de los store badges
             para máxima familiaridad visual. Apunta al listing real. -->
        <a
          href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sinunmango.mobile"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl bg-[#0f172a] px-5 py-3.5 text-white transition-transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 sm:px-6 sm:py-4"
          aria-label="Descargar sinunmango en Google Play"
        >
          <!-- Logo Google Play oficial (4 triángulos de colores) -->
          <svg width="22" height="24" viewBox="0 0 22 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" class="shrink-0">
            <path d="M.84 1.2A2 2 0 0 0 .5 2.31v19.38c0 .4.12.77.34 1.11l10.49-11.4L.84 1.2Z" fill="#5BC8F3"/>
            <path d="m15.5 7.86-3.43 3.73 3.43 3.74 5.04-2.86c1.27-.72 1.27-2.57 0-3.29L15.5 7.86Z" fill="#FFCE3D"/>
            <path d="m12.07 11.59 3.43-3.73L1.5.95 12.07 11.59Z" fill="#EE4647"/>
            <path d="m12.07 11.6L1.5 22.24l14-6.91-3.43-3.73Z" fill="#3BCC70"/>
          </svg>
          <div class="text-left leading-tight">
            <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wide opacity-80">Disponible en</div>
            <div class="text-base font-semibold sm:text-lg">Google Play</div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-[var(--color-ink-muted)]">
        Entrás con Google o email · Free para siempre · Sin tarjeta al registrarte.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero shot: video demo de la app dentro del browser frame.
         Halo decorativo + frame estilo macOS por coherencia visual. -->
    <div class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-3xl lg:max-w-none">
      <!-- Halo decorativo más amplio para que se sienta aireado -->
      <div
        class="bg-brand-gradient absolute -inset-6 rounded-[2rem] opacity-25 blur-3xl"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>

      <!-- Browser frame con video / placeholder -->
      <div
        class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-white shadow-2xl shadow-[color:var(--color-accent2)]/20"
      >
        <div
          class="flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[#f5f5f7] px-4 py-3"
        >
          <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-[#ff5f57]"></span>
          <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-[#febc2e]"></span>
          <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-[#28c840]"></span>
          <div
            class="ml-2 flex h-6 flex-1 items-center justify-center rounded bg-white px-3 text-xs text-[var(--color-ink-muted)]"
          >
            app.sinunmango.com.ar
          </div>
        </div>

        {/*
          ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
          CUANDO TENGAS EL VIDEO DEMO grabado, reemplazá este placeholder por:

          Opción A — mp4 self-hosted en /public/ (RECOMENDADO):
            <video
              controls
              poster="/screenshots/dashboard.jpg"
              preload="metadata"
              class="block aspect-[1570/950] w-full bg-[var(--color-sidebar)]"
            >
              <source src="/demo.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
              <source src="/demo.webm" type="video/webm" />
            </video>

          Opción B — YouTube embed:
            <div class="aspect-[1570/950] w-full bg-black">
              <iframe
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VIDEO_ID?rel=0&modestbranding=1"
                title="Demo de sinunmango"
                class="h-full w-full"
                allow="accelerometer; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
                allowfullscreen
              ></iframe>
            </div>

          Recomendado: self-hosted mp4 — sin tracking de YouTube, sin overlay
          de "videos recomendados" al final, y se ve más prolijo dentro del
          browser frame. Ver docs/landing-video-guion.md para tips de grabación.
          ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
        */}

        {/* Placeholder de video: dashboard.jpg como poster + play overlay.
            Mantiene el aspect ratio del dashboard original (1570/950) para
            que cuando llegue el video real (que asumimos misma ratio) no
            haya layout shift. */}
        <div class="relative aspect-[1570/950] w-full overflow-hidden bg-[var(--color-sidebar)]">
          <img
            src="/screenshots/dashboard.jpg"
            alt="Dashboard de sinunmango: saldo total, indicadores del mes, proyecciones y estado de cuentas"
            width="1570"
            height="950"
            fetchpriority="high"
            decoding="async"
            class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover opacity-70"
          />
          {/* Overlay oscuro + play button gigante */}
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/20 via-black/30 to-black/50">
            <button
              type="button"
              disabled
              class="group relative flex h-20 w-20 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white/95 shadow-xl ring-4 ring-white/30 transition-transform hover:scale-105 sm:h-24 sm:w-24"
              aria-label="Demo en video (próximamente)"
            >
              {/* Play triangle, sutil shift a la derecha para balance óptico */}
              <svg
                width="32"
                height="32"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="currentColor"
                class="ml-1 text-[var(--color-accent2)] sm:h-10 sm:w-10"
                aria-hidden="true"
              >
                <path d="M8 5v14l11-7z" />
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="text-center text-white">
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold sm:text-base">
                Demo en video — próximamente
              </p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-white/70 sm:text-sm">
                Mientras tanto, probala directo en{" "}
                <a
                  href="https://app.sinunmango.com.ar"
                  class="font-medium underline hover:text-white"
                >
                  app.sinunmango.com.ar
                </a>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
